{"ImageContent":{"Description":"位于纽芬兰岛博纳维斯塔半岛的地牢省立公园，长期受到大西洋海浪的塑造与侵蚀。公园最著名的景观“地牢（Dungeon）”实际上是一处巨大的塌陷海蚀洞，其顶部因持续侵蚀而坍塌，形成直通天空的壮观开口。这一地貌生动展示了海洋作用如何在数千年间不断改造坚硬岩石。","Image":{"Url":"/th?id=OHR.DungeonPark_ZH-CN9544093701_1920x1080.webp","Wallpaper":"/th?id=OHR.DungeonPark_ZH-CN9544093701_1920x1200.jpg&rf=LaDigue_1920x1200.jpg","Downloadable":true},"Headline":"大西洋雕琢而成的加拿大","Title":"地牢省立公园, 纽芬兰和拉布拉多省, 加拿大","Copyright":"© Kaitlyn McLachlan/Getty Images","SocialGood":null,"MapLink":{"Url":"","Link":""},"QuickFact":{"MainText":"“地牢”塌陷海洞形成了天然的半封闭空间，海浪拍击时产生的回声会随着海况变化而改变，形成独特的海岸声学现象。","LinkUrl":"","LinkText":""},"TriviaUrl":"/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz&filters=WQOskey:\"HPQuiz_20260701_DungeonPark\"&FORM=HPQUIZ","BackstageUrl":"/search?q=%e5%9c%b0%e7%89%a2%e7%9c%81%e7%ab%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%9b%ad&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate:\"20260630_1600\"+mgzv3configlist:\"BingQA_Encyclopedia_Layout\"","TriviaId":"HPQuiz_20260701_DungeonPark"},"Ssd":"20260701","Name":"DungeonPark","Market":"ZH-CN","Hash":"9544093701","FullDateString":"2026 7月 1","enddate":"20260701"}
